							<p class="card-text">Cras convallis ut turpis vitae facilisis. Morbi eu augue vel quam efficitur rhoncus vitae eget lectus. Cras augue ligula, aliquam ut enim ut, feugiat imperdiet sem.</p>
							<a href="href="{{ path('front.show_post', {
					'page_slug': app.request.get('slug'),
					'post_year': post.dateCreated | date('Y'),
					'post_month': post.dateCreated | date('m'),
					'post_day': post.dateCreated | date('d'),
					'post_slug': post.slug
					}) }}"" class="float-right">Подробнее</a>
